<br>
If you are exiting the arena and follow the wall to your right, you'll pass the barbarian village and then the Aviak 2 spawn in the cove.  Keep following the wall and you'll find his tent at the end of the cove.<br>
<br>
At 14 I would summon my best earth pet, put a fire shield on him and a fire shield on me then nuke Jonah while he fought with my pet.  I would have to mix in heals during the fight. Sometimes he killed my pet but he would be so low that he'd then just kill himself on my fireshield.  He's a monk so he hits fast.<br>
<br>
Once you get your 16 pets, I used a focused Fire pet, the highest one I could get (Hits for 20) and just put him on guard at the entrance to the tent.  A focused, Burnt Out, Fire pet (Level 17, hits for 20) can solo Jonah all day long.  It's a cakewalk to cruise to 20 from there.<br>
<br>
Zallar<br>
